    "en": {
      "name": "Unchained Soul Rage Abominator",
      "effect": "2+ monsters, including a Fiend monster\nIf your opponent Special Summons a monster(s) face-up (except during the Damage Step): You can target 1 of them; destroy 1 Fiend monster you control, and if you do, negate the targeted monster's effects until the end of this turn. When a monster effect is activated on the field and you control a Link-4 or higher \"Unchained\" Link Monster (Quick Effect): You can banish this card from your GY; destroy the monster that activated that effect. You can only use each effect of \"Unchained Soul Rage Abominator\" once per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
